ay, L., A multi-model ensemble approach for assessment of climate change impact on surface winds in France (2009) Clim Dyn, 32, pp. 615-634; Pryor, S.C., Schoof, J.T., Barthelmie, R.J., Empirical downscaling of wind speed probability distributions (2005) J Geophys Res, 110, pp. D19109. , doi: 10. 1029/2005JD005899; Pryor, S.C., Schoof, J.T., Barthelmie, R.J., Winds of change? Projections of near-surface winds under climate change scenarios (2006) Geophys Res Lett, 33, pp. L11702. , doi:10.1029/2006GL026000; Renault, L., (2008) Impact of atmospheric coastal jets on upwelling in the Humboldt Current System, , PhD thesis, Toulouse III University (in French); Renault, L., Dewitte, B., Falvey, M., Garreaud, R., Echevin, V., Bonjean, F., Impact of atmospheric coastal jets on SST off central Chile from satellite observations (2000-2007) (2009) J Geophys Res, 114, pp. C08006. , doi:10.1029/2008JC005083; Sailor, D.J., Hu, T., Li, X., Rosen, J., A neural network approach to local downscaling of GCM output for assessing wind power implications of climate change (2000) Renew Energy, 19, pp. 359-378; Salameh, T., Drobinski, P., Vrac, M., Naveau, P., Statistical downscaling of near surface wind field over complex terrain in southern France (2009) Meteorol Atmospheric Phys, 103 (1-4), pp. 253-265; Seo, H., Miller, A.J., Roads, J.O., The Scripps coupled ocean-atmosphere regional (SCOAR) model, with applications in the eastern pacific sector (2007) J Clim, 20, pp. 381-402; Small, J., Deszoeke, S.P., Xie, S.P., O'Neill, L., Seo, H., Song, Q., Cornillon, P., Minobe, S., Air-sea interaction over ocean fronts and eddies (2008) Dyn Atmospheres Oceans, 45, pp. 274-319; Solomon, S., Qin, D., Manning, M., Chen, Z., Marquis, M., Averyt, K.B., Tignor, M., Miller, H.L., (2007) Climate change 2007: The physical science basis, p. 996. , Cambridge University Press; Uppala, S., Kållberg, P.W., Simmons, A.J., The ERA-40 reanalysis (2005) Quart J Roy Meteor Soc, 131, pp. 2961-3012; Vecchi, G.A., Soden, B.J., Global warming and the weakening of the tropical circulation (2007) J Clim, 20 (17), pp. 4316-4340; von Storch, H., On the use of ""inflation"" in downscaling (1999) J Clim, 12, pp. 3505-3506; von Storch, H., Zwiers, F.W., (2004) Statistical Analysis in Climate Research, , New York: Cambridge Univ Press; Worley, S.J., Woodruff, S.D., Reynolds, R.W., Lubker, S.J., Lott, N., Icoads release 21 data and products (2005) Int J Climatol, 25 (7), pp. 823-842. , doi:10.1002/joc.1166; Wyrtki, K., El Niño-the dynamic response of the equatorial Pacific Ocean to atmospheric forcing (1975) J Phys Oceanogr, 5 (4), pp. 572-584; Xue, H., Wang, Y., Xie, S.P., Effects of the andes on eastern pacific climate: a regional atmospheric model study (2004) J Clim, 17, pp. 587-602; Yeh, S.-W., Kug, S.-J., Dewitte, B., Kwon, M.-H., Kirtman, B.P., Jin, F.-F., El Niño in a changing climate (2009) Nature, 461, pp. 511-514","Goubanova, K.; Laboratoire d'Etudes en Géophysique et Océanographie Spatiale, CNES/CNRS/IRD/UPS, Toulouse, France; email: katerina.goubanova@legos.obs-mip.fr",,,,,,,,09307575,,,,"English","Clim. Dyn.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-79953720624
